description:
This is a 50 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Sleep Relaxation | Let Go of Worries & Strengthen Health' from the channel Michael Sealey.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Welcome to this guided meditation for sleep relaxation to help you let go of worries and strengthen your health, which is especially important during difficult or challenging times.

This guided relaxation experience is a form of sleep meditation with spoken suggestions for complete relaxation, accompanied with a soothing soundscape of gentle background sleeping music.

This sleep healing meditation session combines aspects of guided imagery and visualization, as well as a focus on chakra energy centres of the body, with powerful affirmations for boosting the immune system, for clearing the mind's thoughts, for letting go of negativity, for encouraging overall well being, and for balancing all emotions.
